    {
        "user": "UJBAJNFLK",
        "type": "message",
        "ts": "1767252637.485189",
        "client_msg_id": "bd5fe1f4-9a3c-4579-b75f-d74923f0a7dd",
        "text": "The interface between exploration and explanation is exactly what I am working on, in my <https:\/\/hyperdoc.khinsen.net\/|HyperDoc project>. For a different audience than <@U02QC0PPER3>, but I suspect that many techniques are transferable.\n\nThe initial learning curve is something I see as a major obstacle, as <@U05UK5T7LPP> described. I'll look at Shiffman's work, which I wasn't aware of.",
        "team": "T5TCAFTA9",
        "user_team": "T5TCAFTA9",
        "source_team": "T5TCAFTA9",
        "user_profile": {
            "avatar_hash": "e169f54bbaf8",
